105
00:08:12,980 --> 00:08:14,609
Leave me your WeChat.

106
00:08:14,610 --> 00:08:17,170
I'll take responsibility for all there needs to be.

107
00:08:18,010 --> 00:08:19,550
Like?

108
00:08:19,550 --> 00:08:21,470
Like...

109
00:08:23,410 --> 00:08:24,930
Ms. Jin,

110
00:08:25,890 --> 00:08:27,630
this young...

