When I mentioned responsibility, it meant aside from marriage,

116
00:09:10,489 --> 00:09:14,269
I'll try to fulfill whatever demands you may have.

117
00:09:14,810 --> 00:09:16,330
Heart-breaker.

118
00:09:21,690 --> 00:09:24,389
Thank you. I don't have any demands right now.

119
00:09:24,389 --> 00:09:27,769
All right then. I'll drive you home.

120
00:09:31,850 --> 00:09:35,289
No need for that. Give me a lift to school first.

121
