127
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:18,800
Five, four, three,

128
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:21,220
two, one.

129
00:10:25,280 --> 00:10:30,599
♫ Quick, listen to the voice in your heart ♫

130
00:10:30,599 --> 00:10:37,660
