133
00:10:44,980 --> 00:10:51,120
♫ This time, I'll observe you carefully ♫

134
00:10:57,780 --> 00:10:59,499
School?

135
00:10:59,500 --> 00:11:02,500
Don't be afraid, there are many kinds of schools.

136
00:11:05,020 --> 00:11:07,040
Sorry to trouble you, Miss Jin.

137
00:11:07,040 --> 00:11:09,820
It's all right. It's my pleasure.

138
00:11:14,779 --> 00:11:16,439
Wait a minute.

139
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:28,199
