143
00:11:51,109 --> 00:11:52,910
No.19 High School.

144
00:11:55,570 --> 00:11:57,029
High school?

145
00:11:57,029 --> 00:11:58,569
You're a high school student?

146
00:11:58,570 --> 00:12:02,649
A high school student was not studying hard but appearing in a bar?

147
00:12:02,649 --> 00:12:05,709
The north gate of Southern University along the road to No.19 High School.

148
00:12:05,709 --> 00:12:08,090
It's more convenient to stop there.

149
00:12:09,850 --> 00:12:11,930
Southern University?

150
00:12:11,930 --> 00:12:15,830
Good school. It's hard to get in, isn't it?

151
00:12:17,250 --> 00:12:20,110
It's good as long as he's not a high school student.

152
00:12:23,610 --> 00:12:28,930
Well... Last night, I drank a little too much.

153
00:12:28,930 --> 00:12:31,370
I can't remember some things.

154
00:12:31,370 --> 00:12:34,910
