Qiu Bi, come and pick me up.

161
00:13:12,170 --> 00:13:15,470
I may not be able to drive to the company alive by myself.

162
00:13:20,810 --> 00:13:25,189
- You heard where he asked me to take him this morning, right?
- No.

163
00:13:25,189 --> 00:13:27,050
A school!

164
00:13:27,050 --> 00:13:29,750
- What's wrong with it?
- Why is he going to school?

165
00:13:29,750 --> 00:13:32,410
He's probably going to attend lectures.

166
00:13:33,310 --> 00:13:34,929
Ms. Jin, are you okay?

167
00:13:34,930 --> 00:13:38,929
What did I do to a child?

168
00:13:38,930 --> 00:13:40,389
He's not a child.

169
00:13:40,389 --> 00:13:42,230
He's a college student who is about to graduate.

170
00:13:42,230 --> 00:13:45,140
You've made sure he's not a high school student, so there's no problem.

171
00:13:45,889 --> 00:13:49,069
- It's not illegal to take an undergrad home for the night, right?
- Correct.

172
00:13:49,069 --> 00:13:51,129
My actions didn't damage the company's name, did they?

173
00:13:51,130 --> 00:13:53,730
It wasn't that serious.

174
00:13:53,730 --> 00:13:56,009
Quickly call the company's legal team here to confirm it.

175
00:13:56,010 --> 00:13:57,729
What exactly should I do?

176
00:13:57,730 --> 00:13:59,949
Be accountable to him? Marry him?

177
00:13:59,949 --> 00:14:02,529
Ms. Jin, calm down.

178
00:14:02,529 --> 00:14:04,010
Okay?

179
00:14:07,610 --> 00:14:11,910
Ms. Jin, you've been single since birth for 28 years.

180
00:14:13,370 --> 00:14:15,649
You knew you would lose control after drinking.

181
00:14:15,650 --> 00:14:19,369
Who gave you the courage to take him home last night after getting drunk?

182
00:14:20,250 --> 00:14:26,310
I was a little blinded by his looks.

183
00:14:34,490 --> 00:14:36,490
Are you okay, Miss Jin?

184
00:14:37,750 --> 00:14:41,489
"Big head, big head, no worries about the rain.

185
00:14:41,490 --> 00:14:43,769
Others have umbrellas.

186
00:14:43,770 --> 00:14:46,130
You have a big head."

187
00:14:48,010 --> 00:14:52,030
Do you know what is being crazy after getting drunk?

188
00:14:53,130 --> 00:14:55,050
Being crazy after getting drunk?

189
00:15:07,950 --> 00:15:11,010
Since you're already here, might as well.

190
00:15:12,390 --> 00:15:17,129
Go and find out if that bar drugged my tea.

191
00:15:17,130 --> 00:15:20,529
How else could I have become this crazy?

192
00:15:20,530 --> 00:15:23,009
Ms. Jin, it's really all right.

193
00:15:23,009 --> 00:15:24,769
This matter is a consensual one.

194
00:15:24,770 --> 00:15:27,390
It's still consensual?

195
00:15:27,390 --> 00:15:30,609
Even if it was not consensual, it has already passed.

196
00:15:30,610 --> 00:15:32,930
It's not important anymore, okay?

197
00:15:32,930 --> 00:15:35,049
There is a more important matter for you to handle today.

198
00:15:35,050 --> 00:15:37,630
Your marriage concerning the Gu family. Have you forgotten?

199
00:15:38,490 --> 00:15:40,929
This Old Jin has nothing to do all day.

200
00:15:40,930 --> 00:15:43,630
He's remarried and he's forcing me to get married.

201
00:15:43,630 --> 00:15:44,969
You can't say that about Mr. Jin.

202
00:15:44,970 --> 00:15:47,669
Mr. Jin means well after all. You should understand.

203
00:15:47,669 --> 00:15:49,930
Fine, I got it.

204
00:15:51,010 --> 00:15:52,450
Oh, right.

205
00:15:52,450 --> 00:15:56,090
Let HR send out Wu Youyong's transfer notice today.

206
00:15:57,690 --> 00:16:01,369
I think this Wu Youyong is Mr. Jin's man after all.

207
00:16:01,370 --> 00:16:03,729
If you demote Wu Youyong in such a disguised way,

208
00:16:03,730 --> 00:16:07,010
it will be awkward if you meet Mr. Jin in the future.

209
00:16:07,930 --> 00:16:10,549
He, Jin Xichen, still came to be the Jin family's son as a grownup!

210
00:16:10,549 --> 00:16:13,269
He's not even awkward. Why should I feel awkward?

211
00:16:27,690 --> 00:16:30,789
You asked me to compete fairly with Jin Xichen for the New City Area Development Plan.

212
00:16:30,789 --> 00:16:34,329
I can accept that. But now you're urging me to get married.

213
00:16:34,329 --> 00:16:35,729
Why are you doing this?

214
00:16:35,730 --> 00:16:37,009
I'm getting old.

215
00:16:37,010 --> 00:16:40,370
Someone has to inherit the Jin family's properties. Right?

216
00:16:40,370 --> 00:16:41,549
Who do you want to inherit them?

217
00:16:41,549 --> 00:16:44,670
I'll let whoever gets married first inherit the properties.

218
00:16:44,670 --> 00:16:48,630
So? You want me to go on a blind date with someone from the Gu family?

219
00:16:48,630 --> 00:16:51,470
With the matrimonial alliance between the Gu family and JC. Group,

220
00:16:51,470 --> 00:16:54,329
