223
00:17:00,770 --> 00:17:03,689
Pick one of the three boys from the Gu family.

224
00:17:03,690 --> 00:17:07,829
- After you are married, you will receive 70% of the Jin family's properties.
- 90%.

225
00:17:07,829 --> 00:17:08,929
- 75%.
- 80%.

226
00:17:08,930 --> 00:17:10,550
