227
00:17:10,550 --> 00:17:11,648
It's settled then.

228
00:17:11,649 --> 00:17:14,988
I'll have the legal team draw up the contract and send it to you.

229
00:17:15,649 --> 00:17:17,910
Don't drink so much strong tea.

230
00:17:17,910 --> 00:17:20,890
I'll ask Qiu Bi to get you a new batch tomorrow.

231
00:17:27,850 --> 00:17:33,309
To be honest, I won a dance championship at the school dance competition before.
[Gu Da]

232
00:17:33,309 --> 00:17:39,489
For future banquets, I think I'll be your best dance partner,

233
00:17:39,489 --> 00:17:41,130
Miss Jin.

234
00:17:42,010 --> 00:17:43,550
So impressive.

235
00:17:43,550 --> 00:17:47,389
I heard that Miss Jin likes traditional culture.
[Gu Er]

236
00:17:50,570 --> 00:17:51,769
