237
00:17:51,770 --> 00:17:55,589
Shall we attend the cultural exchange conference together next month?

238
00:17:55,589 --> 00:17:56,969
Okay.

239
00:17:56,970 --> 00:18:00,570
Miss Jin, I have more shares than him.

240
00:18:00,570 --> 00:18:02,089
