246
00:18:17,550 --> 00:18:19,890
- Don't think you're my bro...
- You're like a pig!

247
00:18:20,450 --> 00:18:22,489
I heard that the Gu family has three brothers.

248
00:18:22,490 --> 00:18:25,689
