250
00:18:26,989 --> 00:18:29,289
Not here? Where did he go?

251
00:18:29,290 --> 00:18:30,949
- The school.
- The hospital.

252
00:18:30,949 --> 00:18:33,050
- The hospital.
- The school.

253
00:18:33,730 --> 00:18:36,969
Where exactly did he go? The school or the hospital?

254
00:18:36,970 --> 00:18:42,330
- On his way to school...
- He went to the hospital.

255
00:18:43,950 --> 00:18:45,890
Big Brother! Second Brother!

256
00:18:48,610 --> 00:18:51,250
There's something I'd like to discuss with you.

257
